{"tid":1904462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(留意返) 除左內街有狗拔槍，恆生出面都有！","createTime":"2020-02-29T15:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T04:52:59.000Z","uid":6756,"like":301,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"9272bebf506bb2b88f7baca987bd016658dc31bd","tid":1904462,"uid":6756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"同西洋菜南街差唔多時間點<br />\n恆生銀行出面個到都有便衣狗拔槍！<br />\n<br />\n本身手足掟緊便衣狗車<br />\n點知隻便衣狗阿叔衝落車拎住警棍想打人<br />\n之後俾手足狂掟石頭 隻狗就拔槍出黎<br />\n最後驚到敗走，手足追住架車繼續掟<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所以今晚旺角係有兩單拔槍事件！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"57b66eb14aa9664da07ea3163303c645970ba621","tid":1904462,"uid":304769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n手足加油，手足小心，多謝手足<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1813233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1813233</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5871097976250ab1d105ab877f3c10b999132a6a","tid":1904462,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:49:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4a7f14ca241796042b03a17640a4751c6c5fd8cd","tid":1904462,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8943c9f52958a7c23112b322cbb60e2dcc8939a","tid":1904462,"uid":118888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"058e19599d15fdd1df13fbbf147cecc5a560fe69","tid":1904462,"uid":235277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:54:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c2af828fbecb3cd1da281c5bf89cfaac8ec698","tid":1904462,"uid":67905,"like":3,"dislike":59,"score":-56,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T15:55:19.000Z","msg":"So?"},{"pid":"45ae487957caed5798f39364d1b1917a2a0c5cad","tid":1904462,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02